Title: How EEx Turns Your Template Into HTML
Description: EEx is a templating language and module built into the Elixir standard library, often used by web servers to render dynamic content for a web application. The same concept exists in other language ecosystems, ERB for Ruby, Blade for Laravel/PHP, Pug/Jade for JavaScript.
